ooooooooooh my god..have you ever done something that makes you feel like such a good person and everything you've done in the past is erased b/c of it..well today was like that for me..we took a bunch of toys out to Immokalee for the elementary school kids there..they were SOOOOOOO CUTE!! at the first school a little mentally handicapped boy named Kiko came over and was playing w/ some of us..i gave himi my santa hat and my green beads and he was SO HAPPY! he took pictures of us..then got in some w/ us! SO CUTE!!!..then at the next school a little girl was crying and she came up to me and i asked her what was wrong and she said "this is the best christmas i've ever had"..i lost it i just started balling right there..i think that every year that trip gets better..the look on the kids faces are PRICELESS!..i loved it..wow..but other than that today was pretty good..i'm nervous for finals though..but w/e only a few more days left of Doerr..THANK YOU GOD!!!!..ali's home..fun..but she took my car tonight..not liking that whole thing..meg and i had our famous "talk" on the bus..very good..hehe..hmm nothing else going on really..we all got our pictures taken again..they are okay!..if i knew how to put pictures on here i would..but i dont?!..i've written enough!

allllrighty..so today on the way to school (went in late)..i got a speeding ticket..for $355.50..i was doing 84 mph in a 60 mph zone..and there was construction so the fine was doubled..gay..the workers weren't even working they were just standing around SO FAR AWAY FROM THE ROAD!..this sucks..thats so much freaking money..and the cop was so fat..i think he was just bitter about that..the messed up thing is..every1 around me (like 6 cars) were going just as fast, if not faster than i was?!? but did ne1 else get pulled over?!? NOOOOOOO OF COURSE NOT!!!..the cop was a jerk too..but w/e i was bound to get a ticket on I-75 someday?!?!..well merry christmas to me..

..hm so i went back to school today..definitely made me REALLY tired..it was good to see everyone again..my teachers are actually being pretty cool about everything..that was fun..welty almost cried when i went in there..i love the welty..kinda pissed that one of my "best friends" didn't call me ONCE while i was sick..thats kinda messed up..i think she should stop worrying about herself and start caring about others too..especially if they are supposed to be one of my "best friends"..damn other people call that i barely talk to?!?!..i would just like to say that jessie james was my most favorite person to talk to while i was sick! i love you jessicaaaaaaaaa!! hahaha..oh well! i came home right after school and just passed out until 7..that was nice i was so tired..i'm going to attempt to go to school again tomorrow..see how that goes..ugh..
